title: Question:
author: Junoto
content: Tomorrow, December 2, 2023, is the final of the U-17 World Cup in Indonesia.The final brought together the top country, Germany vs France.Reported from https://bola.tempo.co/read/1803869/prediksi-jerman-vs-prancis-di-final-piala-dunia-u-17-2023-jadwal-kondisi-tim-h2h-perkiraan-susunan-pemainBoth countries are believed to be playing tight and presenting an outstanding game.Looking at the last head to head, the two countries drew 0-0 in the Euro U-17 2023 final.And ended with a penalty shootout which was won by Germany with a score of 5-4.Who will be the favourites for this year's under-17 world cup?
